  <brief_title>Comparing Use of the Glidescope Cobalt to Direct Laryngoscopy in Infants</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Comparison of the Glidescope Cobalt to Standard Direct Laryngoscopy in Infants</official_title>
