  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators seek to prospectively compare intubation with the Glidescope Cobalt to
      Direct Laryngoscopy (DL) in infants.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      We seek to study the intubation characteristics of a new video laryngoscope, the Glidescope
      Cobalt in children less than or equal to 1 yr of age. This evaluation would provide insight
      as to the efficacy of this device in facilitating intubation in infants.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
